Project Title

Image Recognition Web Application Using Django and TensorFlow

Step-by-Step Development Process

1. Project Idea and Planning

The project started with the idea of creating a web-based image recognition system that can allow users to upload images and receive prediction results automatically using Artificial Intelligence.

The aim was to combine:

Frontend web development

Backend programming

Machine learning

Image processing


The system was planned to:

Accept image uploads

Process images with a trained model

Display prediction results to users through a web interface

